These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: peach, zucchini, carrot, lemon, peas, artichoke, pineapple
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, traveling, hiking, board-games, camping, video-games, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, august, april, may, september, february, january
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: metal, punk, country, gospel, techno, blues, r&b
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the fan techno is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the fan blues##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person eating zucchini is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the fan r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the fan gospel is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan country##1
10. the person eating carrot is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating peas##1
12. the person eating peas is the fan metal##1
13. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan country##1
15. the fan blues is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
16. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
17. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
18. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
19. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the fan punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Food      | zucchini  | artichoke        | peas | carrot      | lemon     | peach      | pineapple     |
| Hobby   | traveling | board-games         | woodworking   | puzzles | video-games    | camping | hiking |
| Birthday         | april | september | november | august | january  | february  | may    |
| Music-Genre     | techno  | blues         | metal     | punk    | country | gospel     | r&b     |

