 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person playing chess##1
10. the person watching family movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who growssunflower##2
11. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growslily##1
12. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
13. the person watching horror movies is between the person who growssunflower and the person watching sports movies##2
14. the person playing domino is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
15. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
16. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
17. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person playing poker##1
